# Finance Module Rules

## Architecture
- Single household only.
- True zero-based budgeting: every month starts with budgeted = 0. Positive rollover only.
- Transactions = single source of truth (signed amounts).
- Yjs + PartyKit ONLY for the monthly budget grid (live collaborative editing).
- Everything else uses PocketBase realtime + TanStack Query.
- All balances calculated live from transactions + initialBalance.

## Key Behaviors
- New month → show NewMonthModal with 3 choices (Start Fresh, Copy Last, 3-Month Average).
- Budget Grid must show real-time "Partner is viewing live" when peerCount > 1.
- FAB is a delightful numpad → category → account flow.
- Dashboard must feel emotional (huge To Be Budgeted card, net worth, mini accounts, recent activity).
- Polish phase required: animations, empty states, confetti, micro-interactions.

## Naming & Structure
- All finance files go in src/components/modules/finance/
- Hooks in src/hooks/finance/
- Utils in src/lib/finance/
- Store in src/stores/useFinanceStore.ts

Follow the exact file manifest in FINANCE_MODULE_SPEC.md.